<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><aka>ertguli, martali</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ertguli, martali
 upalia chveni
 ar ghalatʼobs,
 utsvlelia ghmerti

[C1]
   chven aghvapʼqʼrobt
   khelebs
   upals vugalobebt
   shen iqʼavi, shen
   khar...da mokhval

[V2]
 ertguli, martali
 upalia chveni
 ar ghalatʼobs,
 utsvlelia ghmerti

[C2]
   chven aghvapʼqʼrobt
   khelebs
   upals vugalobebt
   shen iqʼavi, shen
   khar...da mokhval</lyrics>
<title>Great is your faithfulness</title>
</song>